---
// FeaturesSection コンポーネント - Modern Design with Cards
---

<section id="features" class="section-padding bg-blue-50">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="mb-6">
        選ばれる理由
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        シータ・クリニカル・サポートが多くの研究者に選ばれる4つの理由
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <a href="#speed-detail" class="card-modern p-8 text-center group hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl cursor-pointer block">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:from-primary/30 group-hover:to-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-3xl filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300">⚡</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">高速対応</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">24時間以内の初回対応でスピーディーなサポートを実現</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary mt-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">詳しく見る →</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href="#recruitment-detail" class="card-modern p-8 text-center group hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl cursor-pointer block">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/20 to-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:from-secondary/30 group-hover:to-secondary/20 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-3xl filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300">🎯</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-secondary transition-colors">高精度マッチング</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">AI技術による最適な参加者選定で効率的な研究を支援</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary mt-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">詳しく見る →</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href="#translation-detail" class="card-modern p-8 text-center group hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl cursor-pointer block">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-secondary/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:from-primary/30 group-hover:to-secondary/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-3xl filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300">🌐</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-gradient transition-colors">多言語対応</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">豊富な外国人サポート実績による安心の多言語サービス</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-primary mt-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">詳しく見る →</p>
      </a>
      
      <a href="#cost-detail" class="card-modern p-8 text-center group hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl cursor-pointer block">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/30 to-accent/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:from-accent/40 group-hover:to-accent/30 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="text-3xl filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300">💰</div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 group-hover:text-accent-foreground transition-colors">コスト効率</h3>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">研究予算に配慮した柔軟な料金体系でコストを最適化</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-accent-foreground mt-4 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">詳しく見る →</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>